name: Marvel Studios Legends
overview: Revisit the epic heroes, villains and moments from across the MCU in preparation for the stories still to come. Each dynamic segment feeds directly into the upcoming series — setting the stage for future events. This series weaves together the many threads that constitute the unparalleled Marvel Cinematic Universe.
tagline: As the universe expands, explore the stories of those destined to become legends.

episodes.name: Wanda Maximoff
episodes.overview: Explore Wanda Maximoff’s growth and the unique bond shaping her destiny.

episodes.name: Vision
episodes.overview: Explore Vision’s quest for humanity and love, capped by selfless sacrifice.

episodes.name: Falcon
episodes.overview: Revisit Sam's journey to becoming The Falcon, and his eventual partnering with The Winter Soldier.

episodes.name: The Winter Soldier
episodes.overview: Relive how Bucky Barnes was twisted into the ultimate assassin, and finally redeemed.

episodes.name: Zemo
episodes.overview: Retrace Zemo’s diabolical scheme to incite a war amongst the Avengers themselves.

episodes.name: Sharon Carter
episodes.overview: Learn how Agent Sharon Carter risked all for Steve Rogers, doing what she knew was right.

episodes.name: Loki
episodes.overview: Retrace Loki's evolution from power-mad villain, to a being with more noble tendencies.

episodes.name: The Tesseract
episodes.overview: Trace the journey of the Tesseract, a powerful object sought by villains and heroes alike.

episodes.name: Black Widow
episodes.overview: Catch up on the history of Agent Romanoff as you prepare for her new film, "Black Widow."

episodes.name: Peggy Carter
episodes.overview: Learn how Peggy Carter aided Captain America and became a founding member of S.H.I.E.L.D.

episodes.name: The Avengers Initiative
episodes.overview: Learn how the "Earth's mightiest heroes" assembled to fight the battles no one else could.

episodes.name: The Ravagers
episodes.overview: Learn the exploits of the Ravagers and trace the unique journey of their leader, Yondu.

episodes.name: The Ten Rings
episodes.overview: Recounts the history of the Ten Rings organization and its mysterious leader, The Mandarin.

episodes.name: Hawkeye
episodes.overview: Recounts how Hawkeye employed his unique skillset to help defeat the evil plans of not just one, but three megalomaniacal beings: Loki, Ultron, and Thanos.

episodes.name: Doctor Strange
episodes.overview: Retrace Doctor Strange's journey from an arrogant neurosurgeon, to the heroic master of sorcery.

episodes.name: Wong
episodes.overview: Retrace Wong's mystical journey from protector of ancient tomes, to protector of worlds.

episodes.name: Scarlet Witch
episodes.overview: Revisit Wanda Maximoff's strange journey from happy homemaker to the dreaded Scarlet Witch.

episodes.name: Thor
episodes.overview: Retrace Thor's journey, from banished Asgardian prince, to one of Earth’s mightiest heroes.

episodes.name: Jane Foster

guest_stars.name: Kat Dennings

episodes.name: Valkyrie
episodes.overview: Recount Valkyrie’s surprising journey: from fallen warrior, to king of New Asgard.

episodes.name: Bruce Banner
episodes.overview: Recounts Bruce Banner’s epic evolution: from man, to monster, to mythic hero.

episodes.name: King T'Challa
episodes.overview: Recall T’Challa's momentous tenure as Wakanda’s most beloved protector, the Black Panther.

episodes.name: Princess Shuri
episodes.overview: Recall Shuri's inspirational journey, from brilliant inventor, to Wakandan warrior.

episodes.name: The Dora Milaje
episodes.overview: Revisit the extraordinary exploits of Wakanda’s fiercest female warriors, the Dora Milaje.

episodes.name: Mantis
episodes.overview: Recall how a lonely empath named Mantis became a Guardian of the Galaxy.

episodes.name: Drax
episodes.overview: Remember the epic journey of Drax, from vengeful Destroyer, to Guardian of the Galaxy.

episodes.name: Ant-Man
episodes.overview: LEGENDS traces those moments big and small that transformed Scott Lang into the tiniest of Earth’s mightiest heroes. Scott faces off against powerful adversaries, meets the love of his life, and becomes the dad he was destined to be. Oh, and it’s the Ant-Man who winds up providing the key to defeating Thanos and saving the universe. He’s kind of a huge deal.

guest_stars.character: Hope van Dyne / The Wasp (archive footage) (uncredited)
guest_stars.name: Evangeline Lilly

episodes.name: Wasp
episodes.overview: All her life, Hope was shielded from the action by her overprotective father, inventor Hank Pym. But when the Pym Particles fell into the wrong hands, Hope reluctantly trained a thief named Scott Lang to become the Ant-Man.

guest_stars.character: Hope van Dyne / The Wasp (archive footage) (uncredited)
guest_stars.name: Evangeline Lilly

episodes.name: Hank & Janet
episodes.overview: Hank Pym and Janet Van Dyne were the original Ant-Man and Wasp, but after an epic show of bravery, Janet was lost forever… or so Hank thought.

guest_stars.character: Hope van Dyne / The Wasp (archive footage) (uncredited)
guest_stars.name: Evangeline Lilly

episodes.name: Peter Quill
episodes.overview: Armed with a cocky attitude and trusty cassette player, Peter Quill, or also known as, Star-Lord, only ever looked out for himself. He stole, punched and kissed his way across the stars. That is, until he found his true family: the Guardians of the Galaxy.

episodes.name: Gamora
episodes.overview: Raised in captivity to be the ultimate warrior by Thanos the Mad Titan, Gamora seemed destined for villainy. But a rebellious turn against her adoptive captor led Gamora to team up with the Guardians of the Galaxy, a band of misfits that would become her chosen family.

episodes.name: Nebula
episodes.overview: For most of her life, Nebula yearned for validation from Thanos, carrying out his evil orders as he conspired to annihilate half the universe. But it was Gamora's love as a sister that finally turned Nebula against their genocidal father, and compelled her to join the Guardians of the Galaxy.

episodes.name: Rocket
episodes.overview: Rocket was the product of illegal genetic experimentation on a raccoon, but after surviving his torturous past, he came out the other side a crack pilot with a snarky mouth and a penchant for making things go boom.

episodes.name: Kraglin
episodes.overview: The second mate in Yondu Udonta's band of swashbuckling Ravagers, Kraglin was almost always a loyal supporter of his blue captain. Over the course of their run-ins with Peter Quill and his oddball crew, Kraglin grew from a faithful follower, to a formidable leader in his own right.

episodes.name: Groot
episodes.overview: Groot is a talking tree that can utter just three words: I am Groot. And only in that particular order. But Groot's also a loyal friend, ferocious warrior and invaluable member of the Guardians of the Galaxy.

episodes.name: Nick Fury
episodes.overview: Track the adventures of Earth’s greatest spy, and the behind the Avengers, Nick Fury.

episodes.name: Maria Hill
episodes.overview: Remember the indispensable agent who defended Earth from annihilation time and time again.

episodes.name: Talos & the Skrulls
episodes.overview: Revisit the story of the Skrulls: a race of oppressed shape-shifters fighting for freedom.

episodes.name: Everett Ross
episodes.overview: Revisit Agent Everett Ross’ unlikely journey, from CIA suit, to valued Wakandan ally.

episodes.name: James Rhodes
episodes.overview: Remember how Col. James Rhodes traded his military uniform for a suit of mechanized armor.

episodes.name: TVA
episodes.overview: Explore the mysterious origins of the Time Variance Authority.

episodes.name: Variants
episodes.overview: What exactly is a Variant?

episodes.name: Carol Danvers
episodes.overview: Retrace Captain Marvel's epic journey as one of the most powerful heroes in the MCU.

episodes.name: Kamala Khan
episodes.overview: Unpack Khan's journey: from a teen who dreams of the Avengers, to a hero names Ms. Marvel.

episodes.name: Monica Rambeau
episodes.overview: Recall Monica Rambeau's unlikely journey: from wide-eyed kid, to full-grown superhero.
